 delhi: The navy is probing the pilferage of information 

 from its computer network but defence minister Pranab Mukherjee 

 said reports that war plans had leaked were bunkum.

 A senior official said evidence 

 had been found that information of the navys acquisition 

 plans for small patrol craft was downloaded about 10 days 

 ago. 

 Betting arrests 

 rajkot 

 (PTI): A father-son duo has been arrested for being allegedly 

 involved in betting during the India-West Indies cricket 

 match on Sunday. Acting on a tip-off police raided their 

 house in Sahakar Nagar in Gujarat and seized a computer 

 and a mobile phone.

 UP crime map

 allahabad 

 (PTI): Uttar Pradesh police will have a digital crime map 

 for the state. The computerised system will relieve officers 

 from going through hundreds of pages to review the crime 

 situation.

 Doordarshan will produce a 110-minute programme to observe the birth centenary of former Prime Minister Lal Bahadur Shastri. The documentary will be in a serial format. 




